seems to welcome anyone who comes out this far.  A strange smell, almost
reminiscent of rotten eggs, comes from the south and, beyond the building, what
looks like clouds of smoke or steam is barely visible.  In any event, the
inside of the building must surely be warmer than the chill of this frozen
land, so investigating it might not be a bad idea.    
