The Hearth~
   Set into the western wall is a massive stone hearth.  Taking up nearly the
entire wall, it is constructed of stones collected from everywhere in the
world.  Obsidian from Fiery Island, jade from Odaishyozen, granite from the
quarries near Toldar's Keep, basalt from Anduin, marble from Nikozia, and even
the rare crystals from Technitzitlan can all be found here.  A shelf above the
fire holds small sculptures of many styles, and the fire itself has the rich
scent of juniper wood.  Cushions scattered on the ground invite people to sit
and watch the fire or read by its light, and low tables further encourage
sitting on the floor.  Many rugs made from the pelts of local animals keep the
floor soft, for it is bare wood underneath.  The great hall lies to the east,
and there is a smaller room to the south.    
~
